{"tid":2193991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"辛尼奧路左膝十字韌帶撕裂！右膝才剛痊愈...","createTime":"2020-09-08T08:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T10:46:45.000Z","uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c944027fe148639553b62ef9b0ce40684089b9f2","tid":2193991,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"據《天空體育》的消息，意大利球星辛尼奧路（Nicolo Zaniolo）又一次遭遇十字韌帶撕裂，這是他八個月以來遭遇的第二次。<br />\n<br />\n　　據報導，辛尼奧路在今年1月重創右膝十字韌帶，完成手術並經過半年休息後，趕得上7月復出再戰意甲。現在他會一直傷停到明年二月，明天將進行手術。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前，意大利與荷蘭的比賽中，辛尼奧路因傷一瘸一拐退場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iE2sm41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiE2sm41.jpg&h=56e6379d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3204a7dbfe5053c2cb919820149805226eac60eb","tid":2193991,"uid":49808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"Roma<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ad370bb09545357b0a885cb4891f7a381a9a43","tid":2193991,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3204a7dbfe5053c2cb919820149805226eac60eb","tid":2193991,"uid":49808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"Roma<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"慘。。踢太公波"},{"pid":"7f8efa2f1fd47520fc047a8b09e15230a6433e39"